title: Polling places for New Bedford election
text: Polling places for New Bedford election Here are the polling places for New Bedford's 2015 municipal elections. Polls will be open Tuesday, Nov. 3, from 7 a.m. to 8 p.m. Comment Posted Oct. 23, 2015 at 4:20 PM Updated at 4:34 PM Posted Oct. 23, 2015 at 4:20 PM Updated at 4:34 PM Â» Social News If you don't know your ward and precinct, you can look it up at the Massachusetts Secretary of State website.
